{"tid":1823124,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"加泰獨立派系: 將與西班牙首相公開對話.  西班牙右翼: 首相出賣國家.","createTime":"2020-01-13T12:05:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T12:45:39.000Z","uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f377d0f213b79e2e50bdce79ca68ca0288fe4112","tid":1823124,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T12:05:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500773-20200103.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500773-20200103.htm&d=x7%2Fg1uS4a%2BT3911x%2BwLoHIm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=be31ff03\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500773-20200103.htm&h=850a10c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500773-20200103.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n加泰獨派投棄權 西班牙政局有望打破僵局<br />\n2020-01-03 HKT 05:15<br />\n<br />\n西班牙政治僵局有望解決，加泰獨派政黨「加泰羅尼亞共和左翼」宣布，黨內13名國會議員，將於稍後對政府的信任投票中棄權，意味社會黨領袖桑切斯可獲得足夠票數，擔任首相一職。<br />\n<br />\n加泰羅尼亞共和左翼說，已經與社會黨達成共識，中央政府同意與加泰自治政府公開對話，解決分歧，因此他們決定棄權，認為雖然道路艱巨而複雜，但是值得。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>西班牙右翼政黨批評桑切斯讓步，認為他成為加泰分離主義分子的人質，出賣國家以換取政權。 </strong>"},{"pid":"2b66351b44ec73ed6c58687a16f1718ed67c2824","tid":1823124,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T12:06:30.000Z","msg":"突破性發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74d97f678c05fddc26027939999d115de02b7d94","tid":1823124,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T12:08:35.000Z","msg":"棄權票換對話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7df940cd6d43d0e4db084d807c601e1cec0546a","tid":1823124,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T12:09:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4e7e369f77ed84b188450053c7fa897acfd78f2","tid":1823124,"uid":37869,"like"